Información importante

   Tipología Master
   Lugar     Milano (Italy)
   Duración  2
     * Master
     * Milano (Italy)
     * Duración:
       2

   Descripción

   MSc. Degree in Marine Science is a 2-year joint degree program offered
   by the University of Milano-Bicocca in partnership with Maldives
   National University. The program provides theoretical knowledge and
   practical experience in the field of marine sciences. The graduates can
   select from 3 main specialization tracks on Bio-ecology, Environment
   and Human Geography.
   The teaching is based on a multi-disciplinary approach integrating
   cutting-edge knowledge and research in this rapidly developing field.
   The program is associated with MaRHE Center in Maldives, which is
   dedicated to scientific research on marine biology, where our students
   get the opportunity to work in scientific labs. Our goal is to provide
   students with the broad expertise on this inter-disciplinary field,
   that better prepares them to address present and future environmental
   challenges.
   (BUTTON) Descripción completa Información importante
   ¿Qué objetivos tiene esta formación?

   Our graduates are equipped with competencies and skills to work across
   diverse positions in organizations focusing on marine processes in the
   public or private sectors as well as in highly specialized research
   fields. The program also provides a solid foundation to pursue doctoral
   studies.
   ¿Qué pasará tras pedir información?

   Admission procedures vary according to the student’s nationality and
   place of residence. For complete clarity concerning different
   pocedures, we invite those interested to consult our website. Since the
   procedure may take several weeks/months of processing, we highly
   recommend you to get in touch with the competent offices as soon as
   possible. PLEASE NOTE: The number of seats available are limited,
   therefore we request you to apply as soon as possible.

   Requisitos: Min. 3 years Bachelor Degree from an accredited
   college/university or its equivalent English Certification: Certificate
   of proficiency in English corresponding to min. B2 level, issued by
   recognized institutions.
   Instalaciones (1) y fechas
   Dónde se imparte y en qué fechas
